channel.title: Need Help Starting Server!
channel.description: I am tired of looking for servers to join, so i want to make a new server. just wanted to throw that out to everyone, lol. but seriously, i need help creating/editing a close-to-perfect runescape server. i want to partner up with someone who i know will hang with it and work on a new runescape server with me now, im not like others and just want some good coders to come and code a server with me, i want someone/(or people) to commit to this server and work on it till it hits close-to-perfect (no server is perfect) so with those few sentences being said, im calling out to whoever thinks they can be helpful. Note: if you dont want to help me, please dont spam this. PS if this should be in a diff section, im sorry in advance! :|
